 The President Muhammadu Buhari on Wednesday, presided over the launch of the emblem appeal fund for the 2021 Armed Forces Remembrance Day celebration.
The event took place at the Council Chamber of the Presidential Villa, Abuja.
Buhari launched the emblem with N10 million.
